<TITLE> Clampdown in Baghaichari after clashes </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Khagrachari, Feb 20 (bdnews24.com)  Local authorities imposed a Section 144 ban on public gatherings in Baghaichari upazila, Rangamati, on Saturday as tensions mounted following clashes between indigenous people and Bangali settlers during which at least 50 houses and shops were torched in the area. bdn
